body:
Please (And Yet I’m Content)

“Are you sure you want this?” Rhodey asked, breathless as he pulled away. “We don’t have to do anything, not if you’re still recovering.”

“I believe I said something about ‘holding your own’,” Tony grinned against Rhodey’s parted lips, “and I am never one to renege on a promise.”

.

summary: I wish you would write a fic where.. the Cloak just keeps depositing Stephen in front of Tony.
question: I wish you would write a fic where.. the Cloak just keeps depositing Stephen in front of Tony.
answer:
This one was so lovely that I just had to write it. Short and sweet. Something we all - but especially Tony and Stephen - deserve after the hell I’ve put them through recently and will again in the very near future. I hope you enjoy this gentle little first kiss scenario as much as I loved writing it.

@mistressstrange - thank you so much for your amazing prompts! They always bring a smile to my face. 💞 And a thousand thanks to @aykin47 for the title! Without that suggestion I would probably still be searching.

This is also my fill for the @ironstrangebingo square “Me.” (07/25)

A Smile That Conquers the Heart

(AO3, 1.365 words)

It was always amusing to watch Stephen fight against his clothing, it really was. Tony watched with barely contained glee as Stephen tried to go into one direction but the Cloak pulled him into the opposite one.

Directly towards Tony.

By the time the Cloak had dragged Stephen in front of Tony he was grinning like a lunatic. “If I didn’t know better I’d think that you want to escape from me while your cape tries its best to keep you near me.” The ‘cape’ in question swatted at him but Tony evaded it with the ease of long practice. But he didn’t resist the impulse to caress the soft fabric for a moment in greeting. It preened in return.

 💫

summary: Threat (Avengers x reader)
body:
Threat (Avengers x reader)

“Avengers I have called you all here because of a mysterious entity Shield has recently discovered. It is unknown if they are a threat or what their powers are. Your job is to find and capture them, and then bring them here to be interrogated.” Nick fury stated to the avengers stationed around the table. He then dismissed them after giving them the threats last known whereabouts.

“ It’s funny how we don’t even know anything about this person. I mean we don’t even know their name or gender.” Tony stayed obviously confused as to why we were going on this mission.

“ It doesn’t matter Fury considers them a threat so we have to capture them.” Natasha stated.

“ I’m with Tony we don’t even know if this person is really threat.” Steve said, which shocked some people because Steve never agrees with Tony.

“Well I guess we’ll find out because we are almost there.” Clint said from the cockpit of the quinjet. The avengers that were there including Steve, Tony, Natasha, and Clint got ready to capture the threat. Bruce, Thor, and Wanda weren’t needed on the mission so they stayed at the tower.

“ Okay guys this should be a simple mission. We knockout the threat with a special dart Bruce made, and then we take them in for interrogation.” Steve said as the jet doors opened. Revealing a abandoned warehouse on the edge of the city. They could hear noise from the inside, not sure of what to expect the avengers slowly crept up to the warehouse. Where Steve proceeded to break open the door using his shield. Then they proceeded to bust into the place, not caring that they weren’t being very discreet.

Inside it looked like a gym, various pieces of equipment could be seen placed about. But the girl in the corner throwing knives at a target caught their attention. Well she wasn’t technically throwing them, because she hadn’t even touched them, so they could only guess she was a telepath. It would of probably been helpful to bring Wanda along. The girl then turned around startled after hearing them bust into the warehouse. When she saw that it was the avengers she dropped the knife, and immediately teleported infront of the avengers startling them.

“Oh boi what did I do this time, is this about the sharks because I really didn’t mean to do that!” The girl said.

“Wait what sharks are you talking about?” Tony asked confused on what she did.

“Oh you don’t know, that’s good, well my names y/n and if you would excuse me I need to get going.” She stated walking toward the doors, but Natasha quickly shot at her to subdue her, but Y/n dodged. She then used her powers to redirect the dart at Natasha, knocking her out.

“ Well that’s my cue to leave, see you later!” Y/n stated as she teleported away. Leaving the avengers that were still awake startled. Steve picked up Natasha and they made their way to the jet, knowing this wouldn’t be the last time that they would see y/n.

Another not so great one shot but hopefully you enjoy it

summary: So when Tony and Stephen get married, we can all pretty safely say that Wong would most likely be the one to walk Stephen down...
question: So when Tony and Stephen get married, we can all pretty safely say that Wong would most likely be the one to walk Stephen down the aisle, right?
answer:
Walk?! Oh no, Stephen is going to float that damn thing down like the drama queen he is. The Cloak will make itself as big and imposing as possible and bring its master into Tony’s arms like Stephen deserves.

But yes, Wong will totally be by his side and watch the whole affair half mortified, half amused and half happy. Yes, that’s a whole 150% of feeling because if anybody is capable of doing that it’s Wong after exposure to Stephen and Tony for so long.

Thanks for making me smile, Anon! 💞

summary: I had a question: so, when Morgan le Fay cursed the Avengers to think they were all ren faire characters, Tony was of pretty...
body:
I had a question: so, when Morgan le Fay cursed the Avengers to think they were all ren faire characters, Tony was of pretty high status as a commander. At least, high enough to get his own bedchambers and actual sheets and curtains. How did Steve just sneak up here? I would assume Tony had guards. Did they just trust Steve had actual business with him?

(And how have I not written a fic about this?
